Usage: replicate.py [options]
  See replicate.py --help for a full list of options.

Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --source-url=SOURCE_URL
                        Url of the source server.
  --target-url=TARGET_URL
                        Url of the target server.
  --source-db=SOURCE_DB
                        Source database name.
  --target-db=TARGET_DB
                        Target database name.
  --continuous          Set as a continuous replication.
  --cancel              Cancel continuous replication.
  --create-dbs          Create databases if missing.
